Dice Statstics Analysis Tool for 8th Edition Warhammer 40,000

To use this tool, please visit http://40k.ghostlords.com/dice/

This tool was created by Jonathan Polley to help enhance your enjoyment of Warhammer 40000. Please direct any feedback to 40k@ghostlords.com.
Warhammer 40000 is copyright Games Workshop Limited.

To install, simply copy all html and js files into a directory and serve on the web, along with any dependencies.

This requires chart.js to function.
http://www.chartjs.org/
